sellerCard.description:
Greeting 
This is Uzair Arshad. I am working as a WordPress Designer and Developer for the last 4 Years.
My skills and experiences range from building responsive websites that work perfect cross-browser to building high-level websites for any industry. I provide 100% guarantee of the quality.

It's important to me to build long-term relationships with my clients, so I'm primarily looking for long-term projects.

description.content:
Want to create a membership website on WordPress or a subscription website or LMS website or facing some error?

I am here to help you in creating a membership website from scratch or add subscriptions to your exciting site.

 

Included Services:

Complete Membership site creation

Setup Membership plans

Creates Pricing Tables

Bug Fixes

Customization

Restriction of desired content

Learndash, Tutor LMS Pro, WooCommerce

Creates Landing Pages for your membership web

LMS Website

 

You can charge your client per day, per month, per year any time of your choice. Your subscription web will be fully functional.


Plugins I work with:

  • Paid Membership Pro
  • Memberpress
  • Learndash
  • Tutor LMS Pro
  • WooCommerce Subscription
  • WooCommerce Membership
  • Elementor
  • And a lot more

 

Why Hire me?

  • Provide consultancy
  • 1 month of support
  • 100% money-back guarantee
  • 24/7 Availability
  • Quality is everything for me and it costs time and hard work.


Please contact me before placing an order

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain name and hosting service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, I am not providing but if you need it, I can suggest you best hosting and domain.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide paid membership plugins for membership or subscription websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, but I suggest you purchase but if you do not then I can provide paid plugins of GPL license.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide ongoing support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide one month of support after the project and after that, you just need to pay me 20$.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I accept PayPal/Stripe payment options on my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, after the completion of your website. I will integrate PayPal and stripe.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started to create a new membership website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need your website login details and, in some cases, your Cpanel and hosting details

reviews.comment: One of my best experiences on Fiverr so far. Very easy to work with and excellent quality. Very creative in the design and followed instructions perfectly adding a lot to the project. Now, let’s build the website. Highly recommended.

Working with this freelancer was an absolute pleasure from start to finish! They took my vision for a professional, user-friendly website and turned it into a reality that exceeded all expectations. The communication throughout the process was exceptional—they kept me updated, answered all my questions promptly, and offered valuable insights to improve the design and functionality of the site. Every detail was crafted with precision, and the final result truly reflects my brand perfectly.

The project was completed ahead of schedule without compromising quality, showcasing their dedication and expertise. From the initial consultation to the final delivery, their professionalism

I hired you Uzair for a few gigs and this is just the first. I am very happy with the logo design. It took a few different tries and he made sure I got what I wanted in my logo from colors, to font, arrangement. I will continue to work with him!

I had the pleasure of working with Uzair  on the development of my new website, and I couldn't be more satisfied with the results. From the very beginning, Uzair demonstrated exceptional professionalism, creativity, and attention to detail. He not only understood my vision but also brought innovative ideas to the table that elevated the project beyond my expectations.
